# Acts 242 — Environment Variables Example
# This site has no required environment variables for production.
# All configuration is in data/site.ts (Formspree endpoints, links, etc.)
# Vercel deployment requires no special environment setup.
#
# If you ever add server-side secrets (e.g. a CMS API key), put them here
# and add them to the Vercel project's Environment Variables dashboard.
#
# Example:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SOME_KEY=your_value_here
